    "en": {
      "title": "Delayed Super Diesel cargo being unloaded, distribution to continue tonight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka's Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera said that there was a delay in unloading the super diesel cargo on Wednesday (24) due to bank clearances.",
        "He said that the unloading commenced on Thursday (25) afternoon.",
        "\"Auto Diesel cargo arriving tonight (25) will commence unloading tomorrow (26). CPSTL Distribution will continue during the night today to make up for the delays,\" tweeted the Minister.",
        "There was a delay in unloading the super diesel cargo yesterday due to bank clearances & discharging has commenced an hour ago. Auto Diesel cargo arriving tonight will commence unloading tomorrow. CPSTL Distribution will continue during the night today to make up for the delays.",
        "Delayed Super Diesel cargo being unloaded, distribution to continue tonight",
        "Time for Ranil to fulfil pledge on repealing PTA made five years ago \u2013 Sumanthiran",
        "Deputy Police Chief testifies in probe on assault on journalists",
        "Multiple unapproved Fuel Storage Tanks at business premises \u2013 Kanchana"
